The Security Council has unanimously increased sanctions against North Korea since 2006 to thwart the funding of Pyongyang’s nuclear and missile program.
Pompeo met with Ri on the sidelines of the UN General Assembly, and afterwards said he would visit Pyongyang again next month to prepare a new summit.
